Description: Hello Team,

We are aware that the New Outlook still doesnt has compatibility with the EPP and we are having improvements on that next patch, but daycoval is unable to capture information on the old outlook as well. Can we schedule a meeting? We can block on any exit point except that one.

Best regards,
What We've Learned Updated: Regex CPF(Brazilian PII) not blocked in old Outlook.
Next Steps Updated: Waiting on logs. Spoke with Eduard - he will ask devs to see

What We've Learned Updated: Regex CPF(Brazilian PII) not blocked in old Outlook.
No policies work in Outlook.
Regex used: 

b[0-9]{1,3}[0-9]{8}b
and
b[0-9]{1,3}[.][0-9]{3}[.][0-9]{3}[-][0-9]{2}b

One with the mask, one without.

Next Steps Updated: Updated Eduard, waiting on next instructions.
